        Banking services
    





                Your banking arrangements should fit with your lifestyle, your plans and your ambitions. We can draw on a full range of services to create a highly personalised solution, designed to work for you.
            







 Investment Outlook
Q3 2017: H2 2017 












            Private banking services
        

            Our dedicated team offers banking services with a personalised focus. The banking services they provide are supported by the HSBC global network. 
        



Transaction banking 


                            Your banking arrangements should fit with your lifestyle, your plans and your ambitions. Our full range of services provide you with a highly personalised solution, designed to work for you globally.
                        



Credit and Debit Cards  


                            Enjoy flexibility and a suite of privileges and services to suit your lifestyle. Whether you are using your debit or credit card, you can complement your lifestyle with a wealth of benefits that suit you and meet your global needs.
                        



Foreign exchange  


                            Focused on you and your family’s financial needs, our foreign exchange team offers an expert, integrated, global foreign exchange service. They also give you the benefit of access to our international network of HSBC businesses.
                        



Margin trading facilities  


                            Margin trading facilities help you to create a more diversified investment portfolio, which can support the management of your long-term investment strategy.
                        



Online banking and reporting  


                            Access your accounts and other useful financial information with HSBC Private Bank’s range of online services.
                        















    
    
