        Financing Services
    





                Financing plays a critical role in managing your wealth strategy. We offer a broad range of lending services for you, your family and your business, so that you can access your assets when you need them.
            







 Managing your wealth













            Financing Services
        

            Credit can be a valuable tool to access the funds you need without drawing on longer-term assets. With the global reach of our business, we provide valuable insights into the local regulations and economic forces that may influence how you borrow and invest.
        



Tailored Lending 


Our tailored lending service gives you customised borrowing options that can increase your liquidity, help protect your wealth and open up new opportunities for you and your family. Our credit advisory specialists have the ability to develop credit solutions to assist in financing and maximising assets that cannot be easily converted into funds. We customise strategies to unlock the potential value of your assets and help you meet your financial goals.



Marketable Securities Backed Finance 


We offer  financing secured by the liquid investments held within your HSBC Private Bank  portfolio. Using your marketable securities to meet short-term liquidity needs  helps pave the way to accomplishing your overall wealth management plans, while  keeping your long-term investment strategy intact. 



Residential Real Estate Finance 


Residential mortgages can be a simple and effective way to borrow, whether you are buying a new property, refinancing a residential mortgage or looking to create liquidity. Our bespoke mortgage service is designed to make the process as easy and flexible as possible. Working with high-net-worth-individuals and families around the world, we offer expertise with cross-border real estate investments.



Specialised Asset Finance  


Using your assets to raise finance opens up a vast range of options. Our experienced and innovative credit advisers can help you find the option that’s right for your needs. We will coordinate and simplify what can often be complex transactions. 






Risk Warning
Your home may be repossessed if you do not keep up repayments on your mortgage.









    
    
